import Home from './components/home/home'
import Login from './components/Login/login';

const routes =[
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Home",
        key: "home",
        route: "/home",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Alphabit",
        key: "alphabit",
        route: "/alphabit",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 1
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Vocabulary",
        key: "alphabit",
        route: "/alphabit",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 1
    }
];

export default routes;
